tachyon.client

Class WorkerFileSystemMasterClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • tachyon.ClientBase
      • tachyon.MasterClientBase
        • tachyon.client.WorkerFileSystemMasterClient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public final class WorkerFileSystemMasterClient
extends MasterClientBase
    A wrapper for the thrift client to interact with the file system master, used by tachyon worker.

    Since thrift clients are not thread safe, this class is a wrapper to provide thread safety, and to provide retries.
